  <facilityDescription><![CDATA[<p><span style="text-decoration: underline;"><strong>Bars &amp; Restaurants</strong></span></p>
<p><strong>The Orsa Maggiore Hotel Restaurant</strong> serves typical recipes from the Aeolian Islands, Sicilian regional cuisine, as well as international dishes. The restaurant is located on a large terrace and serves an a la carte dinner menu. Guests can enjoy lunch by the pool from 1pm to 2.30pm each day. </p>
<p><strong><span style="text-decoration: underline;">General Facilities</span></strong></p>
<ul>
<li>Swimming pool</li>
<li>Bar</li>
<li>Reading room</li>
<li><strong>Free</strong> wifi</li>
</ul>]]></facilityDescription>
