  <roomsDescription><![CDATA[<p><strong>Standard Rooms</strong> are around 18m² and have balconies with views over the garden and pool. They are decorated with a fresh bright colour palette and modern furnishings. </p>
<p><strong>Premium Rooms</strong> are around 19m². They have pool views and are located on the first floor. Each room has its own terrace. The rooms are light and airy with Rattan furnishings. </p>
<p><strong>Junior Suites </strong>have panoramic views across to the volcano and a large terrace. Rooms come with a Nespresso machine and complimentary soft drinks replenished daily.</p>]]></roomsDescription>
